title: Modal Survey 1.9.9.8 - WordPress Poll, Survey & Quiz Plugin
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org Modal Survey WordPress Plugin Nulled provides the opportunity to hear your visitors voice through an attention grabber poll. Unlimited surveys, questions and answers helps to get any information, then display it by a stunning progress bar, beauty pie chart or a simple text format. Creating backup or copy your questionnaire to your other website has never been easier. The Modal Survey WordPress Plugin Free ensures the option to export you poll in JSON format and simply allows to import back the JSON file that has been exported before through the WordPress Plugin admin area. Free Modal Survey WordPress plugin offers the option to specify the number of selectable answers by the users and it is also possible to set the required minimum number of answers for each questions. Modal Survey WordPress Plugin Features Visual Builder on WordPress Administration with Live Preview of the Questionnaire Mobile-friendly & Responsive WordPress Plugin Parallax effect on the Polls during Page Scroll Set Start and Expiry Times for each Questionnaire Choose from Different Styles (Modal / Popup, Embed to your WordPress Page or Post, Open with Click on a Link) Provides Gradient RGB Color Picker on the WordPress Plugin admin Ability to Offer Link / Downloadable Content at the End of the Poll (Force Users to Fill Out to Get the Link) Unlimited Questions and Answers, Reset Counters with One-Click Lock the Screen with the Questionnaire Social Sharing with Various Styles and Modes Request participants name and email at the end of the survey Interactive Tutorial
